[head=2]Pronouncement[/head][/color]

[bold]Station Command Member,[/bold] by filling and stamping this form, you believe that the individual you nominated is qualified for the position and shows the responsibility, respect to the crew, and leadership qualities to properly uphold the honor of the Captain position for the station. Furthermore, you confirm that your nominee is willing and able to take the position of Captain, and is confident in their abilities to lead the Station, and that you are not nominating this individual against their wishes. Finally, you declare that you hold respect and appreciation for your nomination, and are willing to follow their orders, should they be appointed. 

[color=SteelBlue]──────────────────────────────────────[/color]

[color=Gray]This form is only valid if stamped by a member of Station Command. After this form is complete, ensure a copy is sent to both Central Command and the Head of Personnel's office.[/color]
